  "texts": [
    "Specific prompts are available in the supplementary materials.I-2.",
    "Deliberation Facilitator.",
    "This component addresses DC2 (Justification Rationality) and DC5 (Respect and Agreement) by designing corresponding LLM prompts.",
    "In particular, we instruct LLM to (1) Demonstrate a nuanced understanding of the human's statement; (2) analyze the specific content of the person's statement; and (3) provide a thoughtful and critical response.",
    "For detailed prompts, please refer to the supplementary materials.I-3."
  ]
